msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"I've been wanting to tell you something for a while\n"
"now, Makoto..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"And now that it's just the two of us, this is the\n"
"perfect time to confess...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "H-Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Listen, Makoto... Your hoodie is awesome!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "Th-Thanks...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"You have really amazing fashion sense. Now, wearing a\n"
"hoodie under your school uniform..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Your public morals are ruined! Just absolutely ruined!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "S-Sorry! Did I do something wrong...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "The dress code was pretty flexible at my old school..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"Well that's not the case here at Hope's Peak Academy!\n"
"As long as I live, I will protect our morals!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Take off that incredibly stylish hoodie this instant!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "R-Right now!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid "Of course!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "But it's a makeshift hardhat"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "But it's a raincoat"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"But this hoodie doubles as a raincoat! I don't wanna\n"
"get caught by surprise in a thunderstorm!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "You can't fool me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"That hoodie would only protect your head! It's hardly\n"
"a raincoat if it doesn't cover the rest of your body!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "My suggestion is to get an umbrella!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid "G-Good advice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"Now, take off that incredibly stylish hoodie this\n"
"instant!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "But it's a flashlight"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"U-Umm...actually, there's a light built into the hood.\n"
"Kinda like a miner's hat, ya know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid "I need it to keep me safe when it gets dark!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid "That by itself is enough to ruin your morals!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid "A student should head home immediately after school!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"Are you saying you stay out after dark? What are you\n"
"getting up to, Makoto!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"Now do as I say, and take off that incredibly stylish\n"
"hoodie this instant!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid "What's wrong with you, Makoto!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"Are you that determined to keep your hoodie and ruin\n"
"your morals!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Crap, Taka seems to be taking this really seriously...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Well, I'd better come up with a good excuse or I might\n"
"actually have to give him my hoodie...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "But this is the next best thing to a hardhat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "A hardhat...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"Yeah! I mean, this school's really dangerous, ya know?\n"
"There's no telling what might happen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid "So, like...just in case...ya know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Hrmm... You may have a point there..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid "I do! I totally do!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"Well, if it's for your own safety, I suppose I can\n"
"give you special permission, just this once..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"But the instant this school goes back to normal, you\n"
"WILL hand over that amazingly cool hoodie!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid "Y-Yeah, you got it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"Students these days are utterly ignorant of proper\n"
"dress code. It's quite a pain!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid ""
"And frankly, I don't understand youth fashion these\n"
"days anyway!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid ""
"So this is a perfect opportunity for me to teach you\n"
"all about how you should be dressing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Getting fashion advice from Taka isâ€”well, let's just\n"
"say unexpected...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid ""
"I wear this uniform 365 days a year, rain or shine,\n"
"flood or draught, wind and hail and hurricane!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid "Even on your days off? Even on holidays!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid ""
"School itself may observe holidays, but there's no\n"
"such thing as vacation for a student!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid ""
"So as long as I live the life of a student, I will\n"
"always wear my uniform!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"Also, I have ten sets of my uniform, so I always have\n"
"a clean one. There's nothing strange about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Um, no...I'd say wearing your uniform when you're\n"
"not at school is *totally* strange...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'd better keep that to myself, though...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"Hahaha! Trust me, wearing the uniform every day helps\n"
"keep you motivated! You should give it a shot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Taka is exactly the kind of guy I thought he was...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Taka's <CLT><CLT 3>Report Card<CLT><CLT 23> has been updated based on your\n"
"experience with him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your maximum number of <CLT><CLT 3>Skill Points<CLT><CLT 23> has increased!\n"
"Hey, look at you go!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>After we were done, I decided to head back to my room\n"
"for a while...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
